flowchart TD
  START([allocate resourceId + amount + owner + priority]) --> AMT{amount > 0?}
  AMT -->|no| VERR[throw ResourceValidationError]
  AMT -->|yes| LOCK[lock resource]
  LOCK --> RESOLVE[resolve resource + checksum integrity]
  RESOLVE -->|missing| NF[throw ResourceNotFoundError]
  RESOLVE --> QUOTA{quota set?}

  QUOTA -->|owner used + amount > quota| QX[record quota violation\nQuotaExceeded · throw QuotaExceededError]
  QUOTA -->|ok / none| CAP{canAllocate?\nallocated + amount <= capacity - reservation}

  CAP -->|yes| GRANT
  CAP -->|no| PRE[preempt strictly-lower-priority allocations\nlowest priority, then oldest]
  PRE --> PROOM{room now?}
  PROOM -->|yes → each preempted| REL[release victim · ResourceReleased preempted=true]
  REL --> GRANT[create allocation · applyAllocate]
  PROOM -->|no| CONF[record conflict\nthrow ResourceConflictError]

  GRANT --> PERSIST[persist allocation + resource\nupdate accounting stats]
  PERSIST --> EMIT[record allocation + latency\nResourceAllocated]
  EMIT --> END([allocation record + available])

  subgraph RELEASE[release allocationId]
    R1[load active allocation] --> R2[status = released · applyRelease amount]
    R2 --> R3[persist allocation + resource\nResourceReleased]
  end

  subgraph VERIFY[verify]
    V1[recompute resource checksums] --> V2[allocated == sum active allocations?]
    V2 --> V3[issues[] + ResourceVerified]
  end
